text: Mikita Borykau (born 1992) is a Belarusian sprint canoeist.Profile He won a medal at the 2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships.2019 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships results ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male canoeists Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak
